.El
.Pp
All configuration is done via
.Xr sysctl 8
under the device tree, i.e.,
.Va dev.acpi_asus .
.Pp
The driver sends hotkey notifications via
.Xr devd 8 .
You should configure your
.Pa /etc/devd.conf
to suit your needs.
For an example, see the Eee PC entries already present in the system
supplied
.Pa devd.conf .
.Sh SEE ALSO
.Xr acpi 4 ,
.Xr devd 8 ,
.Xr sysctl 8
.Sh HISTORY
